{"tid":2346542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"放工時間觀塘綫列車故障　觀塘站迫爆","createTime":"2020-12-30T10:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T13:55:24.000Z","uid":36494,"like":173,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":120,"replies":[{"pid":"32ea9f3386e329d9941c5bc01b4ba586a963e24d","tid":2346542,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T10:25:41.000Z","msg":"【放工時間觀塘綫列車故障　觀塘站迫爆】<br />\n<br />\n在今日晚上 6 時許放工繁忙時間，港鐵觀塘綫列車服務受阻。在觀塘站，大批市民迫爆月台。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，觀塘綫調景嶺站有列車故障，列車服務受阻。港鐵人員正在處理，請乘客為行程預留充裕時間。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵又指，有關列車現可安排慢速駛離車站，目前觀塘綫的整體行車時間（總站至總站）預計有15 至 20分鐘的額外時間。"},{"pid":"d699a129a8d3f6881562a2c5bb25b1f0681ff209","tid":2346542,"uid":106413,"like":82,"dislike":3,"score":79,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T10:26:45.000Z","msg":"多人多到 又播毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4333214d0b5059eecce76bcc0a6e7a93297b7595","tid":2346542,"uid":127033,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T10:26:49.000Z","msg":"成條線都爆啦<br />\n<br />\n岩收工"},{"pid":"fe1a9373b8c47ef95d9871c94bd2c43091e9d293","tid":2346542,"uid":123920,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T10:27:48.000Z","msg":"黨鐵好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2471b9e9d5c61445e994d6cc614c006f92b24b02","tid":2346542,"uid":66049,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T10:29:01.000Z","msg":"觀塘港鐵群組"},{"pid":"ffcaf8d6b21fff8c11da36c447922ef6b0eca424","tid":2346542,"uid":238773,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T10:30:12.000Z","msg":"執柒左佢喇。"},{"pid":"6b9ebe4eaf72e89ff997db1e4d6bebde72850dc8","tid":2346542,"uid":361751,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T10:30:25.000Z","msg":"港鐵阻塞通勤<br />\n<br />\n又犯國安法"},{"pid":"68da866b6552dfc6954d827c98002d18de885c48","tid":2346542,"uid":194298,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T10:30:48.000Z","msg":"搵人咳幾聲，下班車即刻上到"}